S: hard to pick out for me. Hops in general.  I get some pine. And "freshness" in a sense. Not sure how to explain it. Not a juice bomb to me. 
T: bitter hops. Lovely. Just a hop bomb, but bomb in the most wonderful sense. Grapefruit pith for sure. Nice malt on the finish. Not sweet but bready and maybe a tiny tiny bit pretzely. Flavor lasts and lasts. Long sipper and wonderful. Maybe a little bit of alcohol. Not much at all though. 
F: good carb. Soft. Pillowy. Not dry. Amazing. 
O: the hype is real. Definitely world class. Glad I have 2 more!! 741 charactersMMP126, Mar 29, 2017
