4.9/5  rDev +5.4%look: 4.75 | smell: 4.75 | taste: 5 | feel: 4.75 |  overall: 5Drank half from the can and half from a snifter.  I prefer it from the glass.  
Looks like yellowish everyday IPA in a glass, with a nice foamy head and great lacing.  It looks like a beer is supposed to look.
Smells great.  Citrus and hops, oranges, peels, Grapefruit.  Smells incredible.
Tastes amazing. Once you take a sip you know it was worth the hype.   Incredibly smooth for a DIPA but just enough bite and citrus to stand out.  
Mouth feel is solid...smooth drinking beer with perfect foamy head. 
Overall it right up there with one of my favorite beers.  Definitely worth searching this out if you can.  Glad I had the chance to drink a few. 655 charactersJay_P22, Mar 31, 2016
