Heavy grapefruit and pine hop aroma.  Get orange, mango, pepper, and lemon zest, too.  Light biscuit-y malt.  Just tons of hops.  Orange really grows.
Get the orange and grapefruit in particular on the first sip.  A bit of grassy and earthiness.  Pine hops next, strong but still overshadowed by the orange and grapefruit.  Some biscuit-y, doughy malt.  Noticeable, but not enough to balance the hops.
