4.29/5  rDev -7.7%look: 4.5 | smell: 4.25 | taste: 4.25 | feel: 4.5 |  overall: 4.25I'm going to go similar to Blackboard on this review...
Every time I drink heady, I want it to meet the hype that surrounds it. Most recently I drank it 3 days after canning, and as good as it was, it was still not mind blowing. Don't get me wrong, its a great DIPA in every sense, but there is some heavy competition especially in it's neck of the woods.
Super unfiltered and cloudy/hazy orange in appearance. Super piney and bitter. The IBUs labeled don't match the flavor profile. If Heady is present, I'll never turn one down, but I won't put myself through hell to get a can. A great DIPA, but not the best in the world. 627 charactersJonathannRobert, Jul 21, 2015
