5/5  rDev +7.5%WOW Fantastic.
A - N/A since it's in a can and should stay that way.
S - Citrus, Passion Fruit, Mango, Pineapple, And of course HOPS
T - Sooooo smooth for a DIPA. Scary smooth. You can chug this it is so crisp. I'm having a hard time putting the can down just to do this review. OMG on a Hot day after mowing the grass this would be soooo good. You taste the citrus and the Hop balance. Very little malty flavor. 
