S: Peaches, Apricot, Grapefruit Zest, Guava, Dank, Grassy
T: Grapefruit Zest upfront, leading into Peaches and Guavas, a Bready Malt Middle that serves as a perfect backbone to launch this Hop Drive Brew onto your palate, finishes dry and dank with increased attention to the bitterness balancing all the sweetness and juiciness of this IIPA.
M: Medium-Medium High Body, Chewy
O: 100/100, I've only had a handful of IIPA's on this par and only 2 that were better.  This is the perfect example of what an IIPA should strive to be IMVHO. 
