4.96/5  rDev +6.7%look: 4.25 | smell: 5 | taste: 5 | feel: 5 |  overall: 5I am a stout lover at heart. I have never taken to the hop head beers out there... well that was until I got my first taste of Heady Topper. It is absolutely deserving of the number one beer on beeradvocate. 
Hazy yellow appearance when poured into glass.. of course they tell you right on the can to drink it out of the can but I wanted to see the beer. 
