M: Medium carbonation with a sticky mouthfeel. Slightly astringent. 
O: This is absolutely in the top three IPAs for me. I am about to retry some Pliney here in a couple of days and once I do that I think I will be able to place it. If you like IPAs then this is a must have beer that is worth seeking out. 1,176 charactersTheChiefBrews, Jan 04, 2013
