4.92/5  rDev +5.8%look: 4.5 | smell: 5 | taste: 5 | feel: 4.5 |  overall: 5Presentation: 16 oz. can chilled from the second batch. Huge thanks to Phingdong for giving me this can for nothing. It was definitely appreciated. Poured into my Sam Adams pint glass (I know it says to drink from the can, but I didn't).
