4.97/5  rDev +6.9%look: 4.5 | smell: 5 | taste: 5 | feel: 5 |  overall: 5Heady Topper pours a turbid orange with a soft white, two finger head. An early pour is relatively hazy while the last dregs contain flocculants that reintroduce themselves into suspension. 
