Overall this is a pretty fantastic DIPA right up there with some of the other fine examples of the style, but it definitely has a uniqueness to it with the low carbonation, creamy mouthfeel, incredible smell, hops-galore and easy drinkability. Definitely glad I was able to try it and hoping that this beer does get canned and into regular circulation some day. More people need to experience this one. 1,167 charactersstarrdogg, Dec 09, 2010
